    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was just cleaning my ears with a qtip and i heard this loud pop in my left ear. now it just feels completely blocked and i cant hear anything out of it. it's kind of a ringing sound too. is this just like tinnitus or maybe just a bit of wax buildup? it should go away soon right?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
